body_html:
Interestingly I was just looking at what the status of all this was. The last DaskDataFeeder was made without any collaboration with Dask devs. I am not particularly surprised that it flopped.

I (a Dask dev) have some time for this coming up if anyone on the tensorflow side wants to work together to try things out.
